## **RESTART FRESH:**

1. **Kill all Python processes** (use Task Manager if needed)
2. **Close all Terminal tabs** in VSCode
3. Press **`F5`** to start debugging fresh
4. Submit the form
5. VSCode should pause at the **red dot** breakpoint
6. Now the **debug toolbar buttons will work!**

